2007年和2009年時他參與了歐巴馬的總統競選宣傳活動。也是歐巴馬的國家藝術政策委員會的委員。參演了幾部競選的廣告。<ref>Penn, Kal. [http://www.huffingtonpost.com/kal-penn/open-letter-to-two-undecl_b_101229.html "Open Letter to Two Undeclared College Superdelegates"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/kal-penn/open-letter-to-two-undecl_b_101229.html |date=20110607064556 }}. ''The Huffington Post'', 2008-05-11. Retrieved 2009-04-07.</ref>

